WEBVTT

00:06:58.865 --> 00:07:02.249
that changes when our heart speeds up,
when our muscles tense,

00:07:02.809 --> 00:07:05.706
and all without any obvious change
in our behaviors.

00:07:06.268 --> 00:07:09.006
Alright, I want you to watch
this clip with me.

00:07:09.030 --> 00:07:12.149
Some things might be going on
on the side screens,

00:07:12.173 --> 00:07:15.950
but try and focus on
the image in the front

00:07:15.974 --> 00:07:17.437
and the man at the window.

00:07:19.633 --> 00:07:22.291
(Eerie music)

00:07:27.767 --> 00:07:29.204
(Woman screams)